Technigen Platinum corp said initialresults of a 13-hole drilling program on its R.M. Nicelplatinum property in Rouyn-Noranda, Quebec, indicate extensivenear-surface zones highly enriched in gold, platinum andpalladium.    The metals were found in rocks on the periphery of asulphide deposit.    It said values of up to 0.073 ounce of platinum, 0.206ounce palladium, three pct copper and 4.5 pct nickel were foundover a drill section of 13 feet. Reuter&#3;